PURPOSE:-
--------
To test the behavior of a mobile device which is transmitting data packets and 
becomes disassociated (orphaned) from the PAN coordinator.

SCENARIO:-
---------
Node 1, 2, and 4 are placed in single wireless subnet.
Node 3 is a PAN Coordinator. Other nodes are RFD and Node 2 is mobile.


    2          1
        
         3   
         
         
         4
    
    
CBR is configured between 2 and 1.

CBR 2 1 0 512 1S 1S 5M PRECEDENCE 0


RUN:-
----
Run "<QUALNET_HOME>/bin/qualnet      orphaned-device.config".


DESCRIPTION OF THE FILES:-
-------------------------
1. orphaned-device.app -  QualNet configuration file for application input.
2. orphaned-device.config - QualNet configuration input file.
3. orphaned-device.expected.stat - QualNet statistics collection.
4. README - This file.

